ActFood and Drugs Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Food and Drug Regulations (1431 — Schedule F)
PrecisRegulations amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1431 - SCHEDULE F) in order to add quinine, its salts and derivatives (except in oral dosage form that provides 50 mg or less of quinine base per dosage unit or per daily dose) to Part I of Schedule F to the Food and Drug Regulations.
